2.scbdd.com/server/interact/6538/', '[1] Honig PK, Gillespie BK "Clinical significance of pharmacokinetic drug interactions with over-the-counter (OTC) drugs." Clin Pharmacokinet 35 (1998): 167-71[2] Sommers DK, van Wyk M, Moncrieff J, Schoeman HS "Influence of food and reduced gastric acidity on the bioavailability of bacampicillin and cefuroxime axetil." Br J Clin Pharmacol 18 (1984): 535-9', 1767369485);
